Closes #1498 #1355 This PR adds two new pgRouting functions: - **pgr_lengauerTarjanDominatorTree:** Returns the immediate dominator of all vertices. - **pgr_bipartite:** f graph is bipartite then function returns the vertex id along with color (0 and 1) else it will return an empty set. This is a final merge PR containing commits from several different PRs combined. The intermediate PRs made on the [GSoC-pgRouting](https://github.com/pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting/) repository are as follows: | Description | Pull Requests | | -----------| --------------------- | |pgr_lengauerTarjanDominatorTree|

  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#44

  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#51

pr_body:
Closes #1498 #1355 This PR adds two new pgRouting functions: - **pgr_lengauerTarjanDominatorTree:** Returns the immediate dominator of all vertices. - **pgr_bipartite:** f graph is bipartite then function returns the vertex id along with color (0 and 1) else it will return an empty set. This is a final merge PR containing commits from several different PRs combined. The intermediate PRs made on the [GSoC-pgRouting](https://github.com/pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting/) repository are as follows: | Description | Pull Requests | | -----------| --------------------- | |pgr_lengauerTarjanDominatorTree|
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#40
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#44
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#48
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#51
| |pgr_bipartite |
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#55
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#60
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#64
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#80
| |Code Review & Documentation |
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#112
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#130
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#134
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#135
